text: Jane Elizabeth Leeves (born 18 April 1961) is an English actress. She played Daphne Moon on the NBC television sitcom Frasier from 1993 until 2004. She is also known for her role as Joy Scroggs on TV Land's sitcom Hot in Cleveland. ==References== Category:1961 births Category:Living people Category:English movie actors Category:English television actors Category:English stage actors Category:English voice actors Category:Actors from Essex
